description: This Amazon Alexa Drizzle  Skill Set  mission is to determine if it will rain in the next hour or not in Washington DC.This skill can be used  before going for a walk,shopping,office etc to get weather update for an hour in washington
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Drizzle cloud will it rain after an hour
Alexa ask Drizzle cloud what is the weather in washington
Alexa ask Drizzle cloud Is it raining now
name: Drizzle
shortDescription: A simple Amazon Alexa Skill which calls the Dark Sky API to determine if it will rain in the next hour or not in Washington DC
